<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-26] Wrong quota configuration information</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-26</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the manual at many places one can find information, that to enable quota you need to invoke mkfs.lustre --param mdt.quota_type=ug or appropriate tunefs.lustre command. AFAIK this is wrong, as the parameter name is now mdd.quota_type instead of mdt.quota_type. The &apos;mdd&apos; version is not documented anywhere, so for a quota begginer it&apos;s impossible to enable it correctly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12657">LUDOC-26</key>
            <summary>Wrong quota configuration information</summary>
